{"title":"docker安装elasticsearch","date":"2020-08-09T13:24:20.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Aug 9, 2020","L":"08/09/2020","MM-DD":"08-09"},"link":"2020/08/09/docker-install-elasticsearch","tags":["elasticsearch"],"categories":["elasticsearch"],"updated":"2020-08-12T08:19:13.462Z","content":"<h2 id=\"docker-部署-elasticsearch\">Docker 部署 ElasticSearch<a title=\"#docker-部署-elasticsearch\" href=\"#docker-部署-elasticsearch\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>拉取镜像</li>\n</ul>\n<p>docker仓库里面没有<code>latest</code>标签，目前最新版本是<code>7.8.1</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker pull docker.elastic.co/elasticsearch/elasticsearch:7.8.1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>运行容器</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker run -d --name es -p 9200:9200 -p 9300:9300 -e <span class=\"string\">\"discovery.type=single-node\"</span> elasticsearch:7.8.1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>配置跨域</li>\n</ul>\n<p>首先进入容器</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker <span class=\"built_in\">exec</span> -it es /bin/bash</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>修改配置信息</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 显示当前目录文件和文件夹</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">ls</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 进入config文件夹</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> config</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 显示config下的文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">ls</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 修改elasticsearch.yml文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">vim elasticsearch.yml</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 在最后面加入跨域配置</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">http.cors.enabled: <span class=\"literal\">true</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">http.cors.allow-origin: <span class=\"string\">\"*\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>重启容器</li>\n</ul>\n<p>由于修改了配置信息，需要重启才能生效</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker restart es</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em><strong>现在就可以通过<code>9200</code>端口访问了</strong></em></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>如果你看到如下结果，说明已经成功部署</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight json\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">\"name\"</span> : <span class=\"string\">\"884c4caf7982\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">\"cluster_name\"</span> : <span class=\"string\">\"docker-cluster\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">\"cluster_uuid\"</span> : <span class=\"string\">\"M2J0arXPSA-8QL3JcYNV2g\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">\"version\"</span> : &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">\"number\"</span> : <span class=\"string\">\"7.8.1\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">\"build_flavor\"</span> : <span class=\"string\">\"default\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">\"build_type\"</span> : <span class=\"string\">\"docker\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">\"build_hash\"</span> : <span class=\"string\">\"b5ca9c58fb664ca8bf9e4057fc229b3396bf3a89\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">\"build_date\"</span> : <span class=\"string\">\"2020-07-21T16:40:44.668009Z\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">\"build_snapshot\"</span> : <span class=\"literal\">false</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">\"lucene_version\"</span> : <span class=\"string\">\"8.5.1\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">\"minimum_wire_compatibility_version\"</span> : <span class=\"string\">\"6.8.0\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">\"minimum_index_compatibility_version\"</span> : <span class=\"string\">\"6.0.0-beta1\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">\"tagline\"</span> : <span class=\"string\">\"You Know, for Search\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"docker-部署-elasticsearch-head\">Docker 部署 ElasticSearch-Head<a title=\"#docker-部署-elasticsearch-head\" href=\"#docker-部署-elasticsearch-head\"></a></h2>\n<p><code>ElasticSearch-Head</code>是一个管理界面，可以查看ElasticSearch的相关信息</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker pull mobz/elasticsearch-head:5</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker run -d --name es_admin -p 9100:9100 mobz/elasticsearch-head:5</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<p>通过访问<code>9100</code>端口就可以查看管理界面，然后在文本框输入<code>elasticsearch</code>的访问地址（<code>9200</code>端口），点击连接即可看到相关信息</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"相关链接\">相关链接<a title=\"#相关链接\" href=\"#相关链接\"></a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/jianxuanbing/p/9410800.html\" title=\"Docker 简单部署 ElasticSearch\" target=\"_blank\">Docker 简单部署 ElasticSearch</a></p>\n","next":{"title":"Ubuntu基础操作","link":"2020/06/12/ubuntu-basic-operate"},"plink":"http://blog.arytry.com/2020/08/09/docker-install-elasticsearch/","toc":[{"id":"docker-部署-elasticsearch","title":"Docker 部署 ElasticSearch","index":"1"},{"id":"docker-部署-elasticsearch-head","title":"Docker 部署 ElasticSearch-Head","index":"2"},{"id":"相关链接","title":"相关链接","index":"3"}],"reward":true}